Final Recommendation

If your target clients are ship owners, marine suppliers, and international buyers, the best combination is:

Deep Navy + Silver + White + Small Gold Accent

Avoid:

Bright green
Purple
Orange-heavy designs
Too many container colors in the UI

Those make the site feel cheaper and less corporate.

The overall vibe should feel closer to:

Luxury yacht companies
International shipping corporations
Premium industrial brands

That direction matches your logo and positions Sea Duck Marine Service as an established, trustworthy marine company rather than a local trading business.